keyMappings:
unmapAll

# Find
map / enterFindMode
map n performFind
map N performBackwardsFind

# Modes
map i enterInsertMode
map v enterVisualMode
map V enterVisualLineMode

# Link hints
map f LinkHints.activateMode
map F LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
map Y LinkHints.activateModeToCopyLinkUrl
map t LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewTab
map T LinkHints.activateModeToOpenInNewForegroundTab

# more link behaviors
map h LinkHints.activateMode action=hover
map I LinkHints.activateMode action=focus
map y LinkHints.activateMode action=copy-text
